Class EdgeTypeMapImpl

EdgeTypeMap
public class EdgeTypeMapImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements EdgeTypeMap

Implementation of the EdgeTypeMap interface.

This map is used to define the role of Nodes used in creating a HyperEdge and the role of Nodes added to a HyperEdge. This role will be based on the edge interaction type of the edge to create that contains that Node.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Michael L. Creech
